00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:14,023
Are you well versed in waka?

473
00:37:14,106 --> 00:37:17,777
The two of us did a little studying
since we last met.

474
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:18,861
Just basic stuff.

475
00:37:18,945 --> 00:37:20,529
BEYOND MOUNT OE
