AMANOHASHIDATE

478
00:37:23,824 --> 00:37:25,701
This poem really left an impression on us.

479
00:37:25,785 --> 00:37:27,578
AN INTRODUCTION TO COMPETITIVE KARUTA

480
00:37:27,662 --> 00:37:33,209
"Beyond Mount Oe" was composed on the spot
by a girl as a response to being mocked

481
00:37:33,292 --> 00:37:35,836
for still being dependent on her parents.

482
00:37:38,297 --> 00:37:40,383
"I stand on my own two feet

483
00:37:41,467 --> 00:37:45,513
without the help of my parents," it means.

484
00:37:47,556 --> 00:37:48,683
Did that girl

485
00:37:49,850 --> 00:37:52,812
compose that poem

486
00:37:53,729 --> 00:37:55,564
in order to reclaim her pride?

487
00:37:57,566 --> 00:38:00,069
I… believe so.

488
00:38:09,954 --> 00:38:11,330
And is she…

489
00:38:15,376 --> 00:38:17,962
playing karuta…

490
00:38:20,256 --> 00:38:24,385
to reclaim… herself?

491
00:38:27,096 --> 00:38:28,306
Got it!

492
00:38:39,734 --> 00:38:41,861
-Nice one, Chieri!
-Nice!

493
00:38:42,528 --> 00:38:43,696
Nice, Miss Aizawa!

494
00:38:43,779 --> 00:38:45,990
Let's take the next one too!

495
00:38:46,073 --> 00:38:47,199
Yeah!

496
00:38:58,544 --> 00:38:59,628
Wow.

497
00:39:00,713 --> 00:39:02,465
This is fun!

498
00:39:05,092 --> 00:39:07,011
I don't want it to be over.

499
00:39:10,222 --> 00:39:12,433
Can this just last forever, please?

500
00:39:16,312 --> 00:39:18,064
Maybe that's indulgent.

501
00:39:20,566 --> 00:39:22,318
It is, isn't it?

502
00:39:27,615 --> 00:39:28,532
Thank you.

503
00:39:29,158 --> 00:39:31,410
-Adore win one!
-Nice!

504
00:39:32,411 --> 00:39:34,080
Is this how

505
00:39:34,789 --> 00:39:36,832
the club seniors felt?

506
00:39:40,336 --> 00:39:42,338
And we're already

507
00:39:42,838 --> 00:39:44,757
hurting so much.

508
00:39:50,137 --> 00:39:51,055
Thank you.

509
00:39:51,639 --> 00:39:52,848
Thank you.

510
00:39:55,184 --> 00:39:57,186
-Adore, two wins!
-Nice!

511
00:39:57,269 --> 00:40:01,190
I wish I could go back to that day
and punch myself.

512
00:40:05,319 --> 00:40:07,863
Thank you.

513
00:40:08,406 --> 00:40:11,534
I'm definitely being punished for it now.

514
00:40:11,617 --> 00:40:14,036
-Three wins to Adore!
-Nice!

515
00:40:19,208 --> 00:40:22,002
I should have invested more.

516
00:40:25,256 --> 00:40:27,049
Like Miss Oe.

517
00:40:28,926 --> 00:40:30,886
I should have invested in virtue.

