THE MOON THAT NIGHT DID VANISH

519
00:41:01,292 --> 00:41:03,210
Going round the path

520
00:41:03,294 --> 00:41:05,004
If it is you whom I met

521
00:41:05,087 --> 00:41:07,631
I cannot be sure

522
00:41:12,178 --> 00:41:15,556
I wish I could have met you sooner.

523
00:41:18,225 --> 00:41:19,643
Thank you.

