00:41:28,611 --> 00:41:30,112
Thank you.

527
00:41:30,613 --> 00:41:33,407
-Four wins to Adore!
-Nice!

528
00:41:33,491 --> 00:41:36,368
For behind a single cloud

529
00:41:36,452 --> 00:41:40,873
The moon that night did vanish

530
00:42:18,577 --> 00:42:20,246
Mom! Dad!

531
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:24,833
Thank you for coming.

532
00:42:26,168 --> 00:42:28,462
Starting tomorrow…

533
00:42:33,092 --> 00:42:34,426
Welcome home.

534
00:42:40,307 --> 00:42:43,310
Welcome home, Meguru.

535
00:42:47,565 --> 00:42:48,440
Okay.

536
00:42:50,192 --> 00:42:51,443
I'm… home?

537
00:42:53,862 --> 00:42:54,947
Welcome home.

538
00:43:08,502 --> 00:43:09,837
Miss Oe.

539
00:43:15,467 --> 00:43:16,802
Please take care…

540
00:43:19,888 --> 00:43:21,682
of Meguru.

541
00:43:24,018 --> 00:43:25,978
Teach her all the karuta

542
00:43:26,604 --> 00:43:29,523
she wants to learn.

543
00:43:29,607 --> 00:43:30,858
Please.

544
00:43:32,359 --> 00:43:33,527
Are you sure?

545
00:43:35,571 --> 00:43:36,572
We are.

546
00:43:40,701 --> 00:43:41,785
Certainly.

547
00:43:43,370 --> 00:43:46,248
I'll take good care of Miss Meguru.

548
00:43:49,418 --> 00:43:51,003
Meguru!

549
00:43:51,503 --> 00:43:54,715
-Yay!
-We did it, Mr. Shirano!

550
00:43:54,798 --> 00:43:56,967
What a relief, Miss Aizawa!

551
00:43:57,468 --> 00:43:58,844
Are you crying?

552
00:44:01,889 --> 00:44:04,933
-We can keep playing together.
-Are you crying, Mr. Shirano?

553
00:44:05,017 --> 00:44:06,852
What? No.

554
00:44:17,696 --> 00:44:22,451
FINAL
MIZUSAWA VS. HOKUOH HIGH SCHOOL

555
00:44:30,709 --> 00:44:32,670
Thank you.

556
00:44:34,338 --> 00:44:36,131
Thank you.

557
00:44:36,215 --> 00:44:37,591
One win to Mizusawa.

558
00:44:37,675 --> 00:44:38,926
Nice!

559
00:44:39,009 --> 00:44:41,720
He beat Hokuoh's vice-president
by more than ten cards.

560
00:44:41,804 --> 00:44:42,846
That's crazy.

561
00:44:43,430 --> 00:44:46,892
-Even Hokuoh is in trouble.
-Yes.

562
00:44:46,975 --> 00:44:50,354
And we couldn't get
a single win against them.

563
00:44:51,105 --> 00:44:54,316
The other regulars need to be
watched out for, not just Orie.

564
00:44:54,817 --> 00:44:56,860
Yosuke Shinohara,

565
00:44:56,944 --> 00:44:58,570
a sophomore B-class.

566
00:44:58,654 --> 00:45:02,116
Dynamic takes that make use
of his frame are his weapon.

567
00:45:02,616 --> 00:45:04,535
Miss Oto Yoshino.

568
00:45:05,035 --> 00:45:08,580
An A-class sophomore,
she's Mizusawa's number two player.

569
00:45:09,081 --> 00:45:11,333
Kota Niwano is B-class,

570
00:45:11,417 --> 00:45:14,920
but as their only freshman regular,
he's not to be taken lightly.

571
00:45:15,421 --> 00:45:18,340
Then there's Miss Nagi Tsukiura.

572
00:45:20,050 --> 00:45:23,721
She's improved her game significantly
since that singles match.

573
00:45:31,562 --> 00:45:33,981
So Mizusawa won it, as expected.

574
00:45:34,064 --> 00:45:38,736
But if we're going to go to the All Japan,
we'll have to face them sooner or later.

575
00:45:38,819 --> 00:45:42,030
Yep. We just have to practice
so we can catch up.

576
00:45:42,114 --> 00:45:43,073
That's right.

577
00:45:43,157 --> 00:45:44,241
Darn it!

578
00:45:44,867 --> 00:45:47,161
-I left my towel.
-Huh?

579
00:45:47,244 --> 00:45:49,496
Sorry. You go on ahead.
I'll go look for it.

580
00:45:49,580 --> 00:45:50,581
All right.

581
00:46:14,062 --> 00:46:15,689
Wrong one.

582
00:46:52,226 --> 00:46:53,769
I think that's my towel.

583
00:46:54,686 --> 00:46:55,729
Thank you.

584
00:47:02,069 --> 00:47:03,695
Hey, Nagi!

585
00:47:04,404 --> 00:47:05,405
Hurry up!

586
00:47:05,906 --> 00:47:06,907
Okay.

587
00:47:15,332 --> 00:47:17,543
So you play karuta, then?

588
00:47:23,173 --> 00:47:24,341
Let's…

589
00:47:30,722 --> 00:47:32,057
have a game sometime.

590
00:47:35,602 --> 00:47:37,020
Going round the path

591
00:47:37,104 --> 00:47:39,648
If it is you whom I met
I cannot be sure

592
00:47:40,649 --> 00:47:43,652
For behind a single cloud
The moon that night did vanish

593
00:47:49,324 --> 00:47:52,703
Just as she thought she saw
someone dear from her past,

594
00:47:52,786 --> 00:47:54,663
they disappeared.

595
00:47:55,163 --> 00:47:59,001
Just like the moon
being concealed by the clouds.

596
00:48:10,929 --> 00:48:13,223
UMEZONO HIGH SCHOOL

597
00:48:15,851 --> 00:48:18,729
Is that right?

598
00:48:18,812 --> 00:48:22,649
How nice that Miss Aizawa
is staying in the club.

599
00:48:22,733 --> 00:48:23,775
Yes.

600
00:48:23,859 --> 00:48:28,780
I'll devote even more energy to my role
as club advisor from now on.

601
00:48:30,407 --> 00:48:35,329
Actually, about that…

602
00:48:37,623 --> 00:48:40,626
I'm afraid to inform you

603
00:48:42,753 --> 00:48:46,131
that your contract with us
will be terminated after this year.

604
00:48:47,257 --> 00:48:49,051
-What?
-Don't misunderstand.

605
00:48:49,134 --> 00:48:51,136
It's not about the training camp.

606
00:48:51,219 --> 00:48:53,680
It's nothing to do with that. It's--

607
00:48:53,764 --> 00:48:55,933
-Yes?
-Excuse me.

608
00:48:56,767 --> 00:48:58,769
Excuse me. Please, come in.

609
00:48:58,852 --> 00:49:01,521
-I'm sorry, am I interrupting?
-No, no.

610
00:49:01,605 --> 00:49:06,443
I was just about to talk
about you, Mr. Shima.

611
00:49:10,405 --> 00:49:12,240
Mr. Shima here

612
00:49:12,324 --> 00:49:17,871
is now going to be
returning from paternity leave.

613
00:49:18,372 --> 00:49:22,459
Thankfully, I'm able to start work again
sooner than expected.

614
00:49:22,542 --> 00:49:25,128
Thank you for covering for me.

615
00:49:25,212 --> 00:49:26,838
Oh, not at all.

616
00:49:28,215 --> 00:49:31,385
From the next academic year,

617
00:49:31,468 --> 00:49:34,846
Mr. Shima will be resuming his duties,

618
00:49:35,347 --> 00:49:39,601
including his role with the karuta club.

619
00:49:44,022 --> 00:49:46,817
Subtitle translation by: Lewis Williams
